{"tid":1590882,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[MAGA] 蘋果擬在得克薩斯生產新款Mac Pro","createTime":"2019-09-24T02:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T11:16:19.000Z","uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dc2a48da50f3ae4d4f51a8f61aea7a801ea3f3cc","tid":1590882,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:42:13.000Z","msg":"蘋果擬在得克薩斯生產新款Mac Pro<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001084526\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.ftchinese.com%2Fstory%2F001084526&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obsls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=008cb8b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001084526</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001084526\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.ftchinese.com%2Fstory%2F001084526&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obsls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=008cb8b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001084526</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">蘋果(Apple)證實其新的Mac Pro將在得克薩斯州奧斯汀生產，此前這家iPhone生產商與華盛頓方面討價還價，爭取到了對某些零部件豁免關稅的優待。</span><br />\n<br />\n蘋果股票今年被證明容易受到貿易緊張的影響。華盛頓方面威脅然後實施對3000億美元中國輸美商品徵收10%關稅。<br />\n<br />\n當蘋果爭取關稅豁免時，特朗普總統在7月26日發推文寫道：「蘋果在華生產的Mac Pro 零部件不會獲得關稅豁免。在美國生產，就沒有關稅了！」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n據報導，蘋果曾考慮將這款高端電腦的生產轉移到中國，並探討了將高達30%的製造產能從中國遷至東南亞的想法。</span><br />\n<br />\n蘋果沒有介紹與政府談判的情況，但在周一表示：「在聯邦政府對蘋果需要的某些必要組件免徵關稅後，在美國製造Mac Pro變得可能。」<br />\n<br />\nMac Pro自2013年開始在奧斯汀生產。蘋果表示，按價值計算，新型號的Mac Pro有2.5倍的零部件數量是在美國製造的。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果曾敦促美國政府不要加徵關稅，並在6月警告稱，關稅將「使競爭環境發生傾斜」，有利於該公司的海外競爭對手。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">蘋果周一表示，其在過去一年支出600多億美元「與9000多家國內供應商合作，包括分布於36個州的製造地點。」<br />\n<br />\n蘋果首席執行官蒂姆&bull;庫克(Tim Cook)表示：「Mac Pro是蘋果有史以來最強大的電腦，我們為能在奧斯汀生產它而感到自豪。我們感謝本屆行政當局的支持，讓我們有這個機會。我們深信美國的創新力量。這就是為什麼每一款蘋果產品都是在美國設計和開發的，並由36個州提供零部件，支持美國供應商的45萬個工作崗位，我們將繼續在美國發展壯大。」</span>"},{"pid":"4cbcb749eb076441d4f53c1b1414c63a35f6c601","tid":1590882,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2daac6da5c8a805d56bab011e26fcdecf0ee35","tid":1590882,"uid":160192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:44:09.000Z","msg":"支爆倒數中"},{"pid":"a115f5dfb2fc8527f934638f11393b6319bbdc54","tid":1590882,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4a3164d24e06000178ddab9954ddce37819bb3","tid":1590882,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:45:06.000Z","msg":"收左塊餅,留返比餅碎比支那仔食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b964366c3d999712be37de4ae4ea627e703c6563","tid":1590882,"uid":228955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:45:10.000Z","msg":"支持Made in USA <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvKTfC0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvKTfC0.jpg&h=16de6f79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85ae80b082d0c67e4a0ff7a9aaf2ed8a5c3841fc","tid":1590882,"uid":259329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:46:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c69f1cc7b1f9d154a57b76690838ce419337b72","tid":1590882,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b4524a709226bbd9e655f86f2829d1aab9f42b","tid":1590882,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:05:57.000Z","msg":"真係MAGA"},{"pid":"1d0e847c36d2dcecc2a634c17b79b3944102665b","tid":1590882,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:08:13.000Z","msg":"有牛仔的味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/